Mr. Vice President, one question.

82
00:05:57,250 --> 00:05:58,480
再问一个
One more question!

83
00:05:59,370 --> 00:06:00,480
副总统先生
Mr. Vice President!

84
00:06:00,580 --> 00:06:03,150
