Mr. Vice President, one question, one more question!

85
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:08,860
好的  好的  谢谢你  很好
Okay. Great. Thank you. Great.

86
00:06:09,050 --> 00:06:11,160
好的  谢谢  谢谢你  再见
Okay, good. Thanks, thanks. Bye.

87
