汤姆
Tom.

89
00:06:14,970 --> 00:06:16,910
-她找到它了吗  -没有
- Did she find him? - No.

90
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:18,580
前门开着
Front door was open.

91
00:06:18,940 --> 00:06:20,690
狗不见了  屋里也没人
Dog's not there. No one was there.

92
00:06:20,690 --> 00:06:23,310
汤姆  我太抱歉了  我感觉没别的办法了
Okay, Tom, I am so sorry. I felt like I had no other option.

93
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,690
我发誓
I mean, I swear,

94
00:06:24,690 --> 00:06:27,470
-我真的看见你房子里有人  -我知道
- I saw someone inside your... - No, I know. I know.

95
00:06:27,570 --> 00:06:30,700
要不我们再回去找找  可是
We can go circle back and take another look if you want, but...

96
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:32,470
这不是个好主意
That doesn't sound like a good idea.

97
